## phandle

Specifies a numerical identifier for a node that is unique in the device tree. Used by other nodes to reference this node.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
pio: pinctrl@300b000 {
    compatible = "allwinner,sun50i-h6-pinctrl";
    phandle = <0x01>;
};
```
